==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Culverkey
<hw>Cul"ver*key`</hw> <pr>(-k?`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
bunch of the keys or samaras of the ash tree.</def>
<rj><au>Wright.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An English meadow plant, perhaps the columbine or
the bluebell squill (<spn>Scilla nutans</spn>).</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A girl cropping <qex>culverkeys</qex> and cowslips to make
garlands.</q> <rj><qau>Walton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Culver's root</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Culver's physic</ent>⟦br⟧
